{
  "stem": "7177.1",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So he would always try to get the people on a train to go to Amsterdam or wherever they were going to.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "In fact, the youngest-- I think-- I was about 12, I think.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And since my father was so well-known also by the police and everything-- and we had a particular kind of police during that time-- he didn't always want to go to the border to pick up the people whom he knew were going to come.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "How he always know, I don't know exactly anymore.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "He would send me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I remember that I took a lady from Austria with a little boy who was, at the time, about four or five years old.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They stayed with us for quite some time at home.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I mean, maybe two months or so, something similar to that.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But this was-- that was normal, actually.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "So I was--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Our house was a safe house.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Everybody got something to eat and then was put on a train or on a bus in order to go to the rest of Holland.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My father had the connection.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was-- later on, there became something like Jewish-- I do not remember the-- [DUTCH], that's the Dutch word for it.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So there was a community.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They had all the connections, and they would catch-- or they would, let's say, gather all the Jews that came across the border.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Much, much before.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My father, well, I think he knew what was happening, but-- and specially let's say because in 1940, when the war started, it started in the beginning of May of 1940, we were occupied within two minutes, within two minutes.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because we were not even-- we were not even 10 minutes away from the border.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, definitely.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Oh, definitely.",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
